metadata.name: Free Bird Token #1
metadata.description:
Northern Harrier  
1/1 Bird Token

Free Bird Token #1 was inspired by Andrew Mease's love for photographing birds and playing Magic the Gathering. May this 1/1 flying bird token serve you well in your adventures and lead you to victory.

FREE Bird Token #1 by Andrew Mease is a forever Open Edition as a gift to the world.
